us.avn.ws

Class WsCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • us.avn.ws.WeatherStation
      • us.avn.ws.WsCSV
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AcuRite

    public class WsCSV
extends WeatherStation
    Class: WsCSV Description: provides access to the current (last) values of a weather station output in a CSV file. The "csvConditionNames" provide the offsets into the parameters on the line. time - 0 temperature - 1 barometric pressure - 2 wind speed - 3 wind direction - 4 precipitation - 5
    Author:
    Allan
